<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"The_K-factor_used_by_the_US=
CF">The K-factor used by the USCF</h4><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span =
class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/w/index.php?title=3DElo_rating_system&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D8" =
title=3D"Edit section: The K-factor used by the USCF"><span>edit</span></a>=
<span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The <i>K-factor</i>, in the USCF rating system, can be estimated by divi=
ding 800 by the effective number of games a player's rating is based on (<s=
pan class=3D"texhtml"><i>N</i><sub><i>e</i></sub></span>) plus the number o=
f games the player completed in a tournament (<span class=3D"texhtml mvar" =
style=3D"font-style:italic;">m</span>).<sup id=3D"cite_ref-22" class=3D"ref=
erence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elo_rating_system#cite_not=
e-22"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>21<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]=
</span></a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
