href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dependent_and_independent_variables" =
title=3D"Dependent and independent variables">dependent variables</a>, the =
players' ratings are <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dependent_and=
