tsarticle_40-1" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wik=
i/Elo_rating_system#cite_note-Planeswalkerpointsarticle-40"><span class=3D"=
cite-bracket">[</span>39<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup=
 id=3D"cite_ref-planeswalkerpointsarticle2_41-1" class=3D"reference"><a hre=
f=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elo_rating_system#cite_note-planeswalker=
pointsarticle2-41"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>40<span class=3D"ci=
